item.title: Compiling Error WILL MAKE ADMIN ON MY SERVER IF YOU CAN HELP!
item.dc:creator: @bloodbath32 bloodbath32
item.description:
@bloodbath32 wrote:

@echo off title ******* Compiler "C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.5.0_08\bin\javac.exe" -cp . *.java "C:\Program Files\Java\jre1.5.0_08\bin/java.exe" server pause

And change the 08’s to whatever versions of JDK & JRE you’ve got.
